conbody.p:
(1) Pre-PNMs, Post-PNMs, and IDIQ Order PNMs valued over $10M shall be routed electronically to the Cost and Pricing Branch for review/coordination prior to approval (See


               Contract Document Approval Signature Routing Procedures

         ). Routing to the Cost and Pricing Branch or assigned Contract Price/Cost Analyst is not required when pricing is based on prices/rates are established in base contracts/agreements, when prices are set by law or regulation, or a fair and reasonable price determination can be made by the contracting officer by comparing prices or rates against an existing or previous Government contract where prices are recent and based on an adequately supported fair and reasonable determination.
